UHULUMENI wesifundazwe iKwaZulu-Natal usuhlele usuku lomkhulelo lokukhumbula bonke abashone ngenxa yezikhukhula ezihlasele lesi sifundazwe. Umkhuleko uzoba seDurban Exhibition Center ngo-9 ekuseni ngoLwesine mhla ka-21 Ephreli 2022. “Ukuhlonipha bonke abalahlekelwe yimiphefumulo ngenxa yezikhukhula zakamuva, isifundazwe sizoba nomkhuleko wokududuza nokuzwelana nayo yonke imindeni ethintekayo.” Umkhuleko uzosakazwa bukhoma ezinkundleni zokuxhumana ukuze nabangekho eThekwini bakwazi ukuba yingxenye yawo. 